item.title: CVE-2023-28076|2023-05-16T15:26:19.265Z -- dell -- cloudlink
item.description: CloudLink 7.1.2 and all prior versions contain a broken or risky cryptographic algorithm vulnerability. An unauthenticated remote attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability leading to some information disclosure.
